== UBUZIMA BWITE ==
'''Apotre Mignone''' Ubundi ababyeyi be bamwise '''UMUNEZERO Alice''' ariko baza kumuhimba '''Mignone''' riza no kumufata riba ari ryo rimenyekana cyane. Yavukiye i [[Uburundi|Burundi]] aranahakurira kuko ariho ababyeyi be bari barahungiye.

Apotre Mignone Uyu muvugabutumwa bwiza bwa [[Ubukirisitu|Kristo]] ni umubyeyi w'abana batatu 3 yibyariye ndetse n'anadi benshi arera nkuko abyivugira.niwe wantangije umuryango witwa Women Foundation Ministries n'urusengero rwitwa Nobel Family Church. Akaba ari umugore wa KABERA Eric.<ref>https://hose.rw/kuva-mu-kabyiniro-kugera-mu-rusengero-urugendo-rwo-gukizwa-kwa-apotre-mignone-kabera/</ref>

Akaba yarahawe udushimye hamwe n'ibihembo byinshi, hari nkaho yahawe igihembo cya "'''Sifa Award'''" muri muri compasiyo.<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mignone_Alice_Kabera</ref><ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/42042/women-foundation-ministries-noble-family-church-ku-nshuro-ya-gatanu-yateguye-umunsi-wo-gushima-imana-thanksgivig-in-action-2012--42042.html</ref>

